'''Griv Tershenko''' was a [[Lieutenant/Legends|lieutenant]] with [[New Republic Intelligence Service|New Republic Intelligence]], specifically [[Special Threats Division]]. As an Intelligence agent, one of Tershenko's assignments was to review the [[Black Fleet Crisis]].

